485
00:39:02,030 --> 00:39:02,700
Come on.

486
00:39:02,990 --> 00:39:03,820
This is your exam number.

487
00:39:04,440 --> 00:39:04,820
Good luck!

488
00:39:06,280 --> 00:39:07,090
Three-two-nine.

489
00:39:07,590 --> 00:39:08,340
